{
  "id": "adv_love_2603_08_02",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数年後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "一人で帰る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 57.1666662853
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh005.m4a",
              "text": "悪いけどそういう気分じゃないんだ\n俺は一人で帰るよ",
              "startTime": 57.1666662853,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui003.m4a",
              "text": "そう言って、いつも誘いを断るのよね\nそんなことばかり言ってたら\nそのうち誰からも誘われなくなるわよ",
              "startTime": 62.3666662853,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh006.m4a",
              "text": "それならそれで構わないさ\n俺は一人きりの生活に何の不満もないからな",
              "startTime": 70.7999996186,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 77.2333333333
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――その日の夜",
              "startTime": 78.0666666667,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 79.2666620891
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 79.3333333333
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
              "startTime": 79.4333333333
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh007.m4a",
              "text": "ただいま～\nと言っても、誰もいないんだけど",
              "startTime": 80.0999965669,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "でも、今日はついてたな\n帰りにスーパーで半額シールのついた\n弁当を買えるなんて……",
              "startTime": 85.233328883,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "一人でテレビを見ながら夕飯の弁当を食べて\n冷えたビールを飲む。これが俺の望んだ\n幸せだ。何も不満なんてないさ",
              "startTime": 92.533328883,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "……はぁ\n……猫でも飼おうかな",
              "startTime": 105.8333349865,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "瑠依と帰る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "choice_selection",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "text": "莉央に声を掛ける",
                  "route": []
                },
                {
                  "text": "莉央を無視して帰る",
                  "route": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 113.1000050862
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
              "startTime": 113.2000061035
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "こうして瑠依と一緒に帰るのも久しぶりだな\nとりあえず飲みに行くとして\n瑠依は行きたい店はあるのか？",
              "startTime": 113.9666698457,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui004.m4a",
              "text": "私はどこでも構わないわ\n行き先はあなたが決めて……あら？\nあそこにいるのは莉央さんじゃないかしら",
              "startTime": 121.700003179,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui005.m4a",
              "text": "一緒にいる人は……海外の有名な\n会社の社長だわ。笑顔で握手をして\nどうやら商談がまとまったみたいね",
              "startTime": 130.6333365124,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "海外有名企業との商談か……\nさすが我が社のエース莉央さんだ\n下っ端の俺とは住む世界が違う",
              "startTime": 140.5666698457,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "俺は俺なりに仕事を頑張ってるけど\nやればやるほど莉央さんの凄さが分かって\n二人の距離が遠くなっていく気がするよ",
              "startTime": 149.3333365124,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui006.m4a",
              "text": "{user}君……\nやっぱり、まだ莉央さんのことを……",
              "startTime": 158.200003179,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui007.m4a",
              "text": "あ、莉央さんがこっちに気付いたわ\n私達を見てるけど……どうする？",
              "startTime": 162.6333365124,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 168.1198899906
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（一時は同棲までしていた俺と莉央さんだが\n結局関係は長続きせず、付き合い始めて\n一年足らずで俺達は破局してしまった）",
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi",
      "startTime": 12.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（俺と別れた莉央さんは仕事一筋に打ち込み\nプロジェクトを次々と成功させて\n順調にキャリアを積み上げていた……）",
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8466.666698300001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 19.6965078354
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 20.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi",
      "startTime": 20.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんが新プロジェクトのリーダーに\n任命されたそうよ。今度も成功させたら\n二十代で役員昇進も夢じゃないわ",
      "startTime": 21.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "社運を懸けたプロジェクトを成功させてから\n莉央さんの勢いが止まらないよな\nそれに比べて、俺ときたら……",
      "startTime": 29.8666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんに追いつきたくて\n俺なりに頑張ってきたけど……\nここが俺の限界なのかな……",
      "startTime": 39.3333344778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi",
      "startTime": 46.9333329519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、今日は残業ないんでしょ？\nなら久しぶりに一緒に帰らない？　一杯飲み\nながら美味しいものでも食べましょう",
      "startTime": 46.9333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 55.2683442434
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.0333365124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……ご無沙汰してます",
      "startTime": 170.5333394368,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.3000113171
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 173.3000113171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりね。元気そうで何よりだわ\nこうして話すのはいつ以来かしら",
      "startTime": 173.3000113171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも元気そうですね\n仕事で活躍されている噂はよく聞いてますよ",
      "startTime": 180.6000113171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.1666779837
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、毎日とても充実しているわ\nあ、ごめんなさい。仕事の途中だから\n私はもう行かないと……",
      "startTime": 186.1666779837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 194.3000111897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！\n……一つだけ聞かせて下さい\n莉央さんは今、幸せですか？",
      "startTime": 194.8666739148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.2333466849
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 202.2333466849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ\n仕事で成功する夢が叶って、今とても幸せよ",
      "startTime": 202.2333466849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.2333456677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか。それなら良かった\nお仕事、頑張って下さい\nこれからも応援しています",
      "startTime": 208.2333456677,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10900.003941600005
